org.jppf.node.protocol

Interface JobClientSLA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JobCommonSLA, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JPPFJobClientSLA

    public interface JobClientSLA
extends JobCommonSLA
    This interface represents the Service Level Agreement between a JPPF job and a JPPF client. It determines the state, conditions and order in which a job will be executed.
